Godrej Properties Gains After Approving Fund Raising Plan

-- B y   N i v e d i t h a   R a v i
-- 
2011-10-24T03:50:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-24/godrej-properties-gains-after-approving-fund-raising-plan.html
Godrej Properties Ltd. (GPL)  rose as much
as 4.7 percent in Mumbai after approving a plan to raise as much
as 7.5 billion rupees selling new shares, according to stock
exchange filing on Oct. 21. The shares rose 1.3 percent to 677
rupees at 9:18 a.m. local time  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
